Kim Mai Guest https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kim_Mai_Guest 0 Kim Mai Angela Guest (born August 5, 1969) is an American voice actress of European and Vietnamese descent who is known to speak fluent French and Italian. She is best known for her role as Mei Ling in Metal Gear.
